+ f \cdot g'  \)</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="id871f97df-4492-434d-a5a0-880745b5f587"><p>\( (f \cdot g)' = f' \cdot g' \)</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="idbdfe03d4-560d-43f5-af7c-208cdbf33e30"><p>\( (g \circ h)' = h' \cdot (g' \circ h)  \)</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="idb9e456fe-a80a-4c07-a5dc-e046c0577479"><p>\( (h \circ g)' = g' \cdot (h' \circ g)  \)</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="idf1387d6e-cbb8-4bd0-819a-b130b61c9080"><p>\( (h \circ g)' = g' \cdot (h' \circ g')  \)</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="idda6db671-0bee-46bd-b9b4-220284ac84de"><p>Es gelte \( g(x) \not = 0 \ \forall x \in D_g\). Dann ist \( (\frac{f}{g})' = \frac{f'\cdot g - f \cdot g'}{(g')^2} \)</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="id55f13768-884d-4c2e-a2bd-426a9c889a1b"><p> Es gelte \( g(x) \gt 0 \ \forall x \in D_g\). Dann ist  \(  (g^f)'= (f' \cdot \ln(g) +\frac{f}{g} \cdot g' ) \cdot g^f  \)</p></simpleChoice></choiceInteraction></itemBody><responseProcessing><responseCondition><responseIf><isNull><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1" /></isNull><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><baseValue baseType="identifier">empty</baseValue></setOutcomeValue></responseIf><responseElseIf><match><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1" /><correct identifier="RESPONSE_1" /></match><setOutcomeValue identifier="SCORE"><sum><variable identifier="SCORE" /><variable identifier="MAXSCORE" /></sum></setOutcomeValue><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><baseValue baseType="identifier">correct</baseValue></setOutcomeValue></responseElseIf><responseElse><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><baseValue baseType="identifier">incorrect</baseValue></setOutcomeValue></responseElse></responseCondition><responseCondition><responseIf><and><member><baseValue baseType="identifier">idbdfe03d4-560d-43f5-af7c-208cdbf33e30</baseValue><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1" /></member></and><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKMODAL"><multiple><variable identifier="FEEDBACKMODAL" /><baseValue baseType="identifier">Feedback664732082</baseValue></multiple></setOutcomeValue></responseIf></responseCondition><responseCondition><responseIf><and><member><baseValue baseType="identifier">id871f97df-4492-434d-a5a0-880745b5f587</baseValue><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1" /></member></and><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKMODAL"><multiple><variable identifier="FEEDBACKMODAL" /><baseValue baseType="identifier">Feedback942170480</baseValue></multiple></setOutcomeValue></responseIf></responseCondition><responseCondition><responseIf><and><member><baseValue baseType="identifier">idf1387d6e-cbb8-4bd0-819a-b130b61c9080</baseValue><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1" /></member></and><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKMODAL"><multiple><variable identifier="FEEDBACKMODAL" /><baseValue baseType="identifier">Feedback1662328029</baseValue></multiple></setOutcomeValue></responseIf></responseCondition></responseProcessing><modalFeedback  identifier="Feedback664732082" outcomeIdentifier="FEEDBACKMODAL" showHide="show"><p>a.) Überprüfen Sie, ob die linke und die rechte Seite der Gleichung immer existieren; Sind die betreffenden Funktionen komponierbar ?</p></modalFeedback><modalFeedback  identifier="Feedback942170480" outcomeIdentifier="FEEDBACKMODAL" showHide="show"><p>b.) Achtung, Ableiten ist kein multiplikativer Operator !</p></modalFeedback><modalFeedback  identifier="Feedback1662328029" outcomeIdentifier="FEEDBACKMODAL" showHide="show"><p>c.) In der Kettenregel wird in die Ableitung der äusseren Funktion, die innere Funktion eingesetzt - nicht jedoch die Ableitung der inneren Funktion.</p></modalFeedback></assessmentItem>
